data.description: Secondary waterfront home with acreage on Newman Lake! 3,300 square foot home with 5 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Primary bedroom has walk-in closet and a jetted tub. Partially finished daylight basement leads out to the yard and patio area. Nice deck with views of the lake. Large 3.4 acre lot. Oversized 2 car garage. Private backyard BBQ and firepit area. Lots of room for parking! Includes membership to a sandy community beach and 1 boat slip.
